cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with text embedding and natural language processing. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a semi-supervised representation learning method for text data. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper discusses the effectiveness of text embedding methods for machine learning tasks. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the paper utilizes a large-scale heterogeneous text network to learn the embedding of text. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for text representation learning that has strong predictive power for machine learning tasks.
